<li>b) Consistent and determined</li>
<li>c) Inconsistent</li>
<li>d) Homogeneous<blockquote>
<p><strong>Correct answer: c)</strong> The row $(0\;0\;0\;|\;5)$ represents the equation $0x+0y+0z=5$, i.e. $0=5$, which is a contradiction. The system is <strong>inconsistent</strong>.</p>
</blockquote>
