<li>a) Compute the determinant of the coefficient matrix</li>
<li>b) Identify the unknowns and translate the conditions into equations</li>
<li>c) Apply Gaussian elimination directly</li>
<li>
<p>d) Check whether the system is homogeneous</p>
<blockquote>
